				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the founder of the Latter Day Saint movement.  For other persons, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joseph_Smith_(disambiguation)" title="Joseph Smith (disambiguation)">Joseph Smith (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
