<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Portal icon" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg/16px-Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg" width="16" height="12" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg/24px-Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg/32px-Christus_statue_temple_square_salt_lake_city.jpg 2x" /></a> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portal:Latter-day_Saints" title="Portal:Latter-day Saints">Latter-day Saints portal</a></li>
