<li><span id="CITEREFSmithCowderyRigdonWilliams1835" class="citation">Smith, Joseph, Jr.; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oliver_Cowdery" title="Oliver Cowdery">Cowdery, Oliver</a>; <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sidney_Rigdon" title="Sidney Rigdon">Rigdon, Sidney</a> et al., eds. (1835), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://josephsmithpapers.org/paperSummary/doctrine-and-covenants-1835?dm=image-and-text&amp;zm=zoom-inner&amp;tm=expanded&amp;p=9&amp;s=undefined&amp;sm=none"><i>Doctrine and Covenants of the Church of the Latter Day Saints: Carefully Selected from the Revelations of God</i></a>, Kirtland, Ohio: F. G. Williams &amp; Co, <a href="OCLC.html" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/18137804">18137804</a></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith&amp;rft.btitle=Doctrine+and+Covenants+of+the+Church+of+the+Latter+Day+Saints%3A+Carefully+Selected+from+the+Revelations+of+God&amp;rft.date=1835&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjosephsmithpapers.org%2FpaperSummary%2Fdoctrine-and-covenants-1835%3Fdm%3Dimage-and-text%26zm%3Dzoom-inner%26tm%3Dexpanded%26p%3D9%26s%3Dundefined%26sm%3Dnone&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F18137804&amp;rft.place=Kirtland%2C+Ohio&amp;rft.pub=F.+G.+Williams+%26+Co&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span> <span style="display:none;font-size:100%" class="error citation-comment"><code>|displayeditors=</code> suggested (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:CS1_errors#displayeditors" title="Help:CS1 errors">help</a>)</span>. See <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doctrine_and_Covenants" title="Doctrine and Covenants">Doctrine and Covenants</a>.</li>
<li><span id="CITEREFSmith1842" class="citation">Smith, Joseph, Jr. (March 1, 1842), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.centerplace.org/history/ts/v3n09.htm#706">"Church History [Wentworth Letter]"</a>, <i><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Times_and_Seasons" title="Times and Seasons">Times and Seasons</a></i> <b>3</b> (9): 706–10</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith&amp;rft.atitle=Church+History+%5BWentworth+Letter%5D&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph%2C+Jr.&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Joseph%2C+Jr.&amp;rft.date=March+1%2C+1842&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.centerplace.org%2Fhistory%2Fts%2Fv3n09.htm%23706&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.jtitle=Times+and+Seasons&amp;rft.pages=706%E2%80%9310&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=3" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span>. See <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wentworth_letter" title="Wentworth letter">Wentworth letter</a>.</li>
<li><span id="CITEREFSmith1853" class="citation"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucy_Mack_Smith" title="Lucy Mack Smith">Smith, Lucy Mack</a> (1853), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/NCMP1820-1846,17387"><i>Biographical Sketches of Joseph Smith the Prophet, and His Progenitors for Many Generations</i></a>, Liverpool: S.W. Richards, <a href="OCLC.html" title="OCLC">OCLC</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/4922747">4922747</a></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Lucy+Mack&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.au=Smith%2C+Lucy+Mack&amp;rft.btitle=Biographical+Sketches+of+Joseph+Smith+the+Prophet%2C+and+His+Progenitors+for+Many+Generations&amp;rft.date=1853&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontentdm.lib.byu.edu%2Fu%3F%2FNCMP1820-1846%2C17387&amp;rft_id=info%3Aoclcnum%2F4922747&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pub=S.W.+Richards&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span>. See <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_History_of_Joseph_Smith_by_His_Mother" title="The History of Joseph Smith by His Mother">The History of Joseph Smith by His Mother</a></li>
<li><span id="CITEREFVan_WagonerWalker1982" class="citation"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_S._Van_Wagoner" title="Richard S. Van Wagoner">Van Wagoner, Richard S.</a>; Walker, Steven C. (1982), <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/sbi/articles/Dialogue_V15N02_50.pdf">"Joseph Smith: The Gift of Seeing"</a>, <i><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dialogue:_A_Journal_of_Mormon_Thought" title="Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought" class="mw-redirect">Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought</a></i> <b>15</b> (2): 48–68</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith&amp;rft.atitle=Joseph+Smith%3A+The+Gift+of+Seeing&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+S.&amp;rft.aulast=Van+Wagoner&amp;rft.au=Van+Wagoner%2C+Richard+S.&amp;rft.au=Walker%2C+Steven+C.&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdialoguejournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsbi%2Farticles%2FDialogue_V15N02_50.pdf&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.jtitle=Dialogue%3A+A+Journal+of+Mormon+Thought&amp;rft.pages=48%E2%80%9368&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.volume=15" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><span id="CITEREFVan_Wagoner1992" class="citation"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_S._Van_Wagoner" title="Richard S. Van Wagoner">Van Wagoner, Richard S.</a> (1992), <i>Mormon Polygamy: A History</i> (2 ed.), <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salt_Lake_City" title="Salt Lake City">Salt Lake City</a>: Signature Books, <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number.html" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-941214-79-7" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-941214-79-7">978-0-941214-79-7</a></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJoseph+Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard+S.&amp;rft.aulast=Van+Wagoner&amp;rft.au=Van+Wagoner%2C+Richard+S.&amp;rft.btitle=Mormon+Polygamy%3A+A+History&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.edition=2&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-941214-79-7&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
