ople from Nauvoo, Illinois">People from Nauvoo, Illinois</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:People_from_Windsor_County,_Vermont" title="Category:People from Windsor County, Vermont">People from Windsor County, Vermont</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:People_murdered_in_Illinois" title="Category:People murdered in Illinois">People murdered in Illinois</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Prophet–Presidents_of_the_Community_of_Christ" title="Category:Prophet–Presidents of the Community of Christ">Prophet–Presidents of the Community of Christ</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Prophets_in_Mormonism" title="Category:Prophets in Mormonism">Prophets in Mormonism</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Presidents_of_The_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints" title="Category:Presidents of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints">Presidents of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Smith_family_(Latter_Day_Saints)" title="Category:Smith family (Latter Day Saints)">Smith family (Latter Day Saints)</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:United_States_presidential_candidates,_1844" title="Category:United States presidential candidates, 1844">United States presidential candidates, 1844</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Victims_of_religiously_motivated_violence_in_the_United_States" title="Category:Victims of religiously motivated violence in the United States">Victims of religiously motivated violence in the United States</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Mayors_of_Nauvoo,_Illinois" title="Category:Mayors of Nauvoo, Illinois">Mayors of Nauvoo, Illinois</a></li><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Founders_of_new_religious_movements" title="Category:Founders of new religious movements">Founders of new re